{{#> layout}}
<div>
    <p>Multifactor Authentication has been {{ state }} on your account.</p>
    <p>If this was you, you don't need to take any further action.</p>
    <p>If it wasn't, your account may have been compromised. We recommend changing your password, which will kick out anyone else in your account.</p>
    <p>If you need help, don't hesitate to <a href="mailto:contact@communities.social">reach out to support</a>.<p>
</div>
{{/layout}}
